name: Manky
overview: Guide Manky through each level collecting keys, eggs and grain. Avoid chicks and other nasties and don't fall off the platforms. Collect all keys and six or more eggs. To get more points, collect grain only if Manky's skin is white. When the toilet wall is open, guide Manky to the toilet then sit on it to move on to the next level. You must make it before the time runs out. Good luck!
